BR>Boanerges Thundercry<BR>Erudite Templar of Prexus<BR>Cohort Chalybeius<BR>Cazic Thule Server</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Cland</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">FOr FR hang around KC, lots of FR stuff drops there (ex. Drov mantle, and that no drop bracer)<P><BR>Cland Carbuncle </FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Aliach</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Nother good one if your in GD a lot, keep an eye out for Shardtooth:<P>Crystaline eye: secondary slot:<BR>30hps 30mana 10fire 10cold 10mr.<P>------------------<BR>Aliach Cleric of the <A HREF="http://www.pathofhonor.com" TARGET=_blank>Path</A></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Bala quellious</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Kunzar Cloak +10 Fire<BR>Cloak of the Icebear +20 Cold<BR>Teacher's Sylabus +20 Poison<BR>Stein of Maggok +20 Disease<P>BD Stuff is wonderful, but very very expensive.  Keep an eye open for bargains, they will come around every now and then =)<P>DON'T sell any diamonds, jacinths, or Blue Diamonds you come across. Find a jeweler instead!<P><P>------------------<BR>Bala Illuminaire<BR>56 Cleric<BR><A HREF="http://www.lotuscult.com" TARGET=_blank>Lotus Cult</A> <BR>Quellious</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Dikmer</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Saw a level 60 Cleric friend of mine, and she had a Bloodstained Mantle on her shoulders.<P>I couldn't figure out why, when she is not broke and has UBER stuff everywhere else (Blue Diamond Braclets, Sarnak Shield, Full Donal's/EM, Water Sprinkler, etc, etc.<P>Then I saw this thread and realized she had it for the +10 Magic Resist.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Sobchak</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" 