 DR <BR>Mammoth Cloak, Molten Cloak; CR and FR <BR>Kylong Gaunts <P>Then you have the high end stuff : <BR>Weight of the Gods <BR>Heirophant Cloak<BR>Necklace of Superiority or Dragon Totems <BR>Lodizal Shield <BR>various dragon shields; Red, White, Green <BR>Halo of Enlightenment (drool)<BR>Gauntlets of Infuse (see above)<BR>If you are going to quest for armor the best resists appear to be on the Skyshrine ones (dragon faction though--eep)<P>As you can see there are a TON of things out there. Some at the top of your wish list some that only fit in your gear set up depending on what you have at the time and who you are grouped with. Enlightenment makes up a lot of wisdom folks  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"> No Im not a loot monger I just like to keep up on whats what. <P>Belkram of BB <P>PS Aaldiana, Alierias, and Deww need to attend every Cazic run; they HAVE Halos !! *chuckle*</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
